    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 1st level, you are naturally suited for hunting prey. You gain a Bite attack, which deals 1d6 Piercing damage and uses your Strength or Dexterity for attack and damage rolls. Additionally, As an Action, you may consume a deceased human regaining a number of RC Cells equal to the rank of the creature (Minion: 1, Standard: 3, Elite: 5, Solo: 10). You can regain a number of RC Cells in this way equal to 3 times your Constitution modifier per long rest.</p>",
